{"tid":960280,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽驗到有白內障","createTime":"2018-12-29T09:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T14:53:55.000Z","uid":54035,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad19f55b24c9b129bd186a14a7cc39871d69c9a","tid":960280,"uid":54035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"有日同阿媽去配眼鏡 <br />\n個視光師話佢左眼白內障 都幾熟下 <br />\n要做手術 私家做就預兩萬以內<br />\n佢話政府可能會見得返兩成視力 會早d幫佢做<br />\n因為唔知轉介信係轉去驗眼驗到有事再排手術<br />\n驚排好耐 時間長咗驚手尾長<br />\n所以諗住去盲人輔導會度驗下先<br />\n但係打極電話都無人聽 留言又無人覆...<br />\n而家book咗寶血度驗<br />\n知唔知寶血驗眼o唔ok?<br />\n如果真係有事 係咪可以轉介去政府做手術？"},{"pid":"02341f62c43caf40960d39309b4b2d7aafd701b4","tid":960280,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"排左政府先 再搵私家"},{"pid":"f0dd6bec93a976e5f4d72055d5fda87d20698516","tid":960280,"uid":186096,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"之前係一間眼科診所做過<br />\n啲醫生姑娘都好好人架<br />\n雖然比佢地炒咗我魷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間診所係油麻地 叫寶視眼科中心<br />\n價錢都係15k-20k左右 醫生會睇情況<br />\n兩位醫生都好多人讚手勢好<br />\n<br />\n你試下預約去睇<br />\n唔係打手 純粹想比多個選擇你"},{"pid":"0ffe0b486280c3204ca40b6d7e411a2e0890de03","tid":960280,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"小問題"},{"pid":"9da9a052135a6e4bf5aa1141b719ef27e9bb8e83","tid":960280,"uid":54035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02341f62c43caf40960d39309b4b2d7aafd701b4","tid":960280,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"排左政府先 再搵私家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:39:25.000Z","msg":"驗眼定做手術？<br />\n驚排得好耐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa50c3bd9e300b9a6fefdbd92f66b1b58c8a0c57","tid":960280,"uid":54035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0dd6bec93a976e5f4d72055d5fda87d20698516","tid":960280,"uid":186096,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"之前係一間眼科診所做過<br />\n啲醫生姑娘都好好人架<br />\n雖然比佢地炒咗我魷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間診所係油麻地 叫寶視眼科中心<br />\n價錢都係15k-20k左右 醫生會睇情況<br />\n兩位醫生都好多人讚手勢好<br />\n<br />\n你試下預約去睇<br />\n唔係打手 純粹想比多個選擇你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我阿媽驗下睇下係咪咁嚴重<br />\n真係做手術都想搵個好"},{"pid":"e97f3dfa59b8e1eacf093403aa0cb2a4468149e2","tid":960280,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"好普遍，有啲眼科醫生直頭係診所幫你搞埋，唔洗入醫院<br />\n<br />\n唔係咩大手術<br />\n<br />\n不過留意做完手術可能會有posterior capsule opacification <br />\n<br />\n詳情問下醫生啦"},{"pid":"c8b04bc051c367d4b105423c5cb9cfab675bd107","tid":960280,"uid":54035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ffe0b486280c3204ca40b6d7e411a2e0890de03","tid":960280,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"小問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:44:46.000Z","msg":"快搞掂就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3761de9ddddae94ea1604d30b96f0b2c09fd0d","tid":960280,"uid":54035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e97f3dfa59b8e1eacf093403aa0cb2a4468149e2","tid":960280,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"好普遍，有啲眼科醫生直頭係診所幫你搞埋，唔洗入醫院<br />\n<br />\n唔係咩大手術<br />\n<br />\n不過留意做完手術可能會有posterior capsule opacification <br />\n<br />\n詳情問下醫生啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"我睇過話手術好快就做完 但阿媽都60幾<br />\n係有少少緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱啱check咗 話係愈後生做就愈大機會有<br />\n希望到時順順利利啦"},{"pid":"3239926387121da01f212579cda59acc1bbb3340","tid":960280,"uid":207109,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇到白內褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW多啲陪吓媽媽 <br />\n媽媽得一個 唔好失去左先後悔"},{"pid":"116fb7dfc7ef269d26c52bbf9455d4b3c0601210","tid":960280,"uid":175079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"而家係好普遍，媽媽仲有冇番工？如果有，政府會排你快D做"},{"pid":"bb9589daf27c362bb67f2503602309881a782876","tid":960280,"uid":40532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:16:16.000Z","msg":"去瑪麗醫院 眼科排全港最快，唔好去九龍排"},{"pid":"5d7fdadb97079fc3f4b62c5fe05237ffde9ea691","tid":960280,"uid":195396,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"建議你即刻做咗先。白內障算係小手術，喺私家眼科診所做都無問題。<br />\n有閒錢唔放心可以比多啲book醫院做。<br />\n<br />\n拖得耐理論上唔會對視力有咩大問題。最大問題係未做嗰段時間捱得辛苦，睇到嘢同睇唔到嘢嘅mindset可以差好遠。<br />\n<br />\n利申 廿三歲 兩隻眼都做咗白內障手術<br />\n有兩年時間乜都睇唔到<br />\n拖咗兩年喺心態上嘅影響遠大於視力影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7665c72677b102edaa4694910c1da6f188664a27","tid":960280,"uid":129030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d7fdadb97079fc3f4b62c5fe05237ffde9ea691","tid":960280,"uid":195396,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"建議你即刻做咗先。白內障算係小手術，喺私家眼科診所做都無問題。<br />\n有閒錢唔放心可以比多啲book醫院做。<br />\n<br />\n拖得耐理論上唔會對視力有咩大問題。最大問題係未做嗰段時間捱得辛苦，睇到嘢同睇唔到嘢嘅mindset可以差好遠。<br />\n<br />\n利申 廿三歲 兩隻眼都做咗白內障手術<br />\n有兩年時間乜都睇唔到<br />\n拖咗兩年喺心態上嘅影響遠大於視力影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:33:39.000Z","msg":"我33歲都做左，小手術，休息一星期就得"},{"pid":"9e3de6ddbaf21d619b428bc489b46cef8652abe8","tid":960280,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7665c72677b102edaa4694910c1da6f188664a27","tid":960280,"uid":129030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d7fdadb97079fc3f4b62c5fe05237ffde9ea691","tid":960280,"uid":1